alTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">contra el <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">abuso) est\u00e1<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\"> al <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">centro de la filosof\u00eda <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">y la pr\u00e1ctica <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">de Good <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">Neighbors<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\"> y representa el compromiso de <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/goodneighbors.cl\/descarga-guia-derechos-nino-chile\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">\u202f<\/span><\/a><\/span><a href=\"_wp_link_placeholder\"><span class=\"FieldRange SCXW11038824 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW11038824 BCX8\" lang=\"ES-CL\" xml:lang=\"ES-CL\" data-contrast=\"none\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">proteger los derechos de <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">ni\u00f1as,<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><span class=\"TextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\" lang=\"ES-CL\" xml:lang=\"ES-CL\" data-contrast=\"none\"><a href=\"_wp_link_placeholder\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\"> ni\u00f1os y adolescentes<\/span><\/a><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\"> (NNA)<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\"> as\u00ed como de las personas adultas que <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">apoyan nuestro trabajo<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">, mientras procuramos <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">construir un futuro sustentable con participaci\u00f3n activa de <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">todas y todos<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">. Good Neighbors <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">se toma muy en serio<\/span> <span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">esta responsabilidad y <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">su <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">obligaci\u00f3n para <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">con <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">los derechos de <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">NNA<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW11038824 BCX8\">, como su principal prioridad, aplicando esta pol\u00edtica fielmente tanto a nivel nacional como internacional.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW11038824 BCX8\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1f4e612 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"1f4e612\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/goodneighbors.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Politica-de-Salvaguardia-de-Ninos-y-Adultos-Good-Neighbors-VR-25.02.22.pdf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Descarga la Pol\u00edtica<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e690870 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e690870\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Prop\u00f3sito<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-256063b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"256063b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">El objetivo principal de la pol\u00edtica de salvaguardia es proteger a todas las personas, y especialmente a NNA de cualquier tipo de abuso, maltrato o dona en las actividades de Good Neighbors.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:384,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">El segundo prop\u00f3sito es evitar que el personal y otras personas relacionadas con el trabajo de Good Neighbors participen, condonen o de cualquier otra forma se involucren en conductas impropias. . Incluso la simple sospecha puede causar un da\u00f1o inmenso a los proyectos y la imagen p\u00fablica de Good Neighbors en general.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:384,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17cb711 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"17cb711\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Principios B\u00e1sicos<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-694e871 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"694e871\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&q